---
source: crates/runtime/tests/metadata/mod.rs
expression: explain_met_last_modified_filtered
---
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: met_last_modified.id ASC NULLS LAST, met_last_modified.last_modified ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |   Filter: met_last_modified.last_modified = TimestampMicrosecond(1728538620000000, Some("UTC"))                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |     TableScan: met_last_modified projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified], partial_filters=[met_last_modified.last_modified = TimestampMicrosecond(1728538620000000, Some("UTC"))]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [id@0 ASC NULLS LAST, last_modified@5 ASC NULLS LAST]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |     FilterExec: last_modified@5 = 1728538620000000                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |       BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |         DataSourceExec: file_groups={3 groups: [[hive_partitioned_data/year=2022/month=1/day=1/data_0.parquet, hive_partitioned_data/year=2022/month=1/day=2/data_4.parquet], [hive_partitioned_data/year=2022/month=3/day=3/data_2.parquet, hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet], [hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=4/day=1/data_3.parquet]]}, projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified], file_type=parquet |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
